     2вҶ’ * Viewport State Machine (XState v5)
     3вҶ’ *
     4вҶ’ * Manages viewport state including zoom, pan, and LOD (Level of Detail).
     5вҶ’ * Follows FSM pattern for deterministic, testable state management.
     6вҶ’ */
     7вҶ’
     8вҶ’import { createMachine, assign } from 'xstate';
